<div id="cardParticipationInfo" class="card participation-info">
	<h3 class="registration__section--header">Event Participation</h3>
	<p class="registration__section--summary">
		Events include swim meets, virtual championships, and open water races. If you selected "I prefer not to say" for your sex, you cannot select a membership with an event license. Even though you can select an event license later in your My Account, we still suggest you select an event license now if you are unsure.
	</p>
	<div class="form-group">
		<label class="control-label font-weight-bold col-xs-12">Do you plan on participating in events?</label>
		<div class="col-xs-12">
			<span class="help-block help-block--participationInfo">Please select your participation preference</span>
		</div>
		<div class="col-xs-12">
			<label class="radio-label" for="participationInfoYes" style="cursor:pointer;">
				<div class="radio-container">
					<input type="radio" name="participationInfo" id="participationInfoYes" value="yes">
					<span class="radio__placeholder"></span>
				</div>
				Yes
			</label>
			<label class="radio-label" for="participationInfoNo" style="cursor:pointer;">
				<div class="radio-container">
					<input type="radio" name="participationInfo" id="participationInfoNo" value="no">
					<span class="radio__placeholder"></span>
				</div>
				No
			</label>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="form-group competition-category" style="display:none;">
		<label class="control-label font-weight-bold col-xs-12">Competition Category</label>
		<div class="col-xs-12"><span class="help-block help-block--competitionCategory">Please select your competition category</span></div>
		<div class="col-xs-12">
			<label class="radio-label" for="competitionCategoryMens" style="cursor:pointer;">
				<div class="radio-container">
					<input type="radio" name="competitionCategory" id="competitionCategoryMens" value="mens-open">
					<span class="radio__placeholder"></span>
				</div>
				Mens/Open
			</label>
			<label class="radio-label" for="competitionCategoryWomens" style="cursor:pointer;">
				<div class="radio-container">
					<input type="radio" name="competitionCategory" id="competitionCategoryWomens" value="womens">
					<span class="radio__placeholder"></span>
				</div>
				Womens
			</label>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="form-group national-recognition" style="display:none;">
		<label class="control-label font-weight-bold col-xs-12">Do you want to be included in National Competitive Recognition Programs?</label>
		<div class="col-xs-12"><span class="help-block help-block--nationalRecognition">Please select an option</span></div>
		<div class="col-xs-12">
			<label class="radio-label" for="nationalRecognitionYes" style="cursor:pointer;">
				<div class="radio-container">
					<input type="radio" name="nationalRecognition" id="nationalRecognitionYes" value="yes">
					<span class="radio__placeholder"></span>
				</div>
				Yes
			</label>
			<label class="radio-label" for="nationalRecognitionNo" style="cursor:pointer;">
				<div class="radio-container">
					<input type="radio" name="nationalRecognition" id="nationalRecognitionNo" value="no">
					<span class="radio__placeholder"></span>
				</div>
				No
			</label>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="form-group competition-certification" style="display:none;">
		<label class="control-label font-weight-bold col-xs-12">Certification of Competition Category</label>
		<div class="col-xs-12">
			<span class="help-block help-block--CompetitionMembership">Please select certification of competition category option</span>
		</div>
		<label class="radio-label radio-label--inline col-xs-12" for="competitionMembershipYesInput" style="cursor:pointer;">
			<div class="radio-container">
				<input type="radio" name="CompetitionMembership" id="competitionMembershipYesInput" value="yes">
				<span class="radio__placeholder"></span>
			</div>
			I certify that my sex assigned at birth corresponds with the competition category selected OR I have selected the male competition category.
		</label>
		<label class="radio-label radio-label--inline col-xs-12" for="competitionMembershipNoInput" style="cursor:pointer;">
			<div class="radio-container">
				<input type="radio" name="CompetitionMembership" id="competitionMembershipNoInput" value="no">
				<span class="radio__placeholder"></span>
			</div>
			<div>I DO NOT certify that my sex assigned at birth corresponds with the competition category selected. (A USMS representative will contact you to discuss participation and eligibility procedures.)</div>
		</label>
	</div>

	<div class="form-group agree-terms-competition" style="display:none;">
		<div class="col-xs-12">
			<span class="help-block help-block--agree-terms-competition">You need to agree to the terms to continue.</span>
			<label id="agree-terms-competition__label" class="checkbox-label" for="agree-terms-competition">
				<div class="checkbox-container">
					<input type="checkbox" name="agree-terms-competition" id="agree-terms-competition" value="">
					<span class="checkbox__placeholder"></span>
				</div>
			</label>
			<span class="font-weight-bold">I acknowledge that the <a href="~/link.aspx?_id=B1745ABEA65D4D65AC6F848A0E3E413A&amp;_z=z">Interim USMS Policy on Participation in the Men's/Open and Women's Competition Category and Eligibility for Official Recognition Programs</a>&nbsp;allows members to participate in the competition category that reflects the sex with which they identify; however, members will not be included in Recognition Programs in the female competition category unless their sex assigned at birth is also female. Members participating in the male competition category will be eligible for recognition. Eligibility is subject to all other USMS rules and regulations.</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
